{
  "stem": "17135.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 16.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and-- and I said, if-- what difference does it make?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Let's get killed by-- by-- by-- by shooting, at least, like man.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Like human beings.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I-- my brother, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe-- we all ran.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My father didn't run.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The elderly people stayed there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- God will help them, so to speak.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They-- they really believed in God, that-- that eventually will save them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that-- and-- and they did not kill us.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They calmed us down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Even they gave us food.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I remember this like yesterday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "To calm us down, that-- to show, so to speak, their good will, and-- and told us, next day, you will be all sent by train to a labor camp in Poland.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's the order that came from the headquarters, the Gestapo.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You aren't the only ones.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "All the Jews in all the concentration camps are being deported to the east.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So you didn't have to say goodbye to your father--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "All of.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--because you thought he was coming with you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they didn't say Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we knew that-- not Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Auschwitz was really a Polish military castle, you know that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But Birkenau was built only '41.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And how was Birkenau built?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The former [NON-ENGLISH] of [NON-ENGLISH] became the commandant of Auschwitz, took with him 50 [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Before [NON-ENGLISH] means [NON-ENGLISH], professional killer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They had a green angle.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were all-- look what the Nazis did-- when they built the concentration camps, they took all the prisoners in the-- in the prisons-- that had-- they were convicted for capital offenses-- rapists, murderers-- and made them kapos and Blockalteste in the camp.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They became the big shots in the camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were themselves prisoners, enjoyed a lot of privileges, and stole half the Russians.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
